eu.slipo.athenarc.triplegeo

Class ReverseExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.slipo.athenarc.triplegeo.ReverseExtractor

  • public class ReverseExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility for validating RDF datasets and reconverting them into geographical files (reverse transformation). LIMITATIONS: Currently only supporting CSV (delimited) files and ESRI Shapefiles. TODO: Include support for GEOJSON?
    Version:
    1.7
    Author:
    Kostas Patroumpas
